@NickeZ Although it's a much smaller buffer needed to implement this, still I want both <3.

Has there been any work started here, or maybe people are hesitant because this will clearly want to use the same facilities that #124 uses? I'm might be interested in trying to write up a PR for this though.

P.S. If that means diving into helping with the scrollback stuff, I'm all for that, especially considering scrollback is the only thing keeping me from using standard release of alacritty instead of a patched version.
